snippet.title: Phantasie I Gameplay - C64 - Longplay
snippet.description:
Phantasie I Gameplay - C64 - Longplay

We take a stroll through Lord Wood's castle to retrieve the water rune. This can only be obtained after visiting all three magic pools. Each member of the party must be immersed in the pools.

Not a playthrough, just gameplay footage of a great vintage game. Some parts were left out as the video is quite long as it is. No commentary, only some text added.

If you have any questions, please ask.

#phantasie #c64 #commodore
